{"id":213,"date":"2012-02-23T16:40:22","date_gmt":"2012-02-23T16:40:22","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.mirandanet.org\/mirandamods\/?page_id=213"},"modified":"2012-03-06T08:17:20","modified_gmt":"2012-03-06T08:17:20","slug":"the-future-of-learning-series-2","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/mirandamods\/2011-2012\/the-future-of-learning-series-2\/","title":{"rendered":"The future of learning series (2)"},"content":{"rendered":"<h2>Integrating 21st century skills into the classroom<\/h2>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/mirandamods\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/02\/C21.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-302\" title=\"C21\" src=\"http:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/mirandamods\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/02\/C21-300x229.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"229\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/mirandamods\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/02\/C21-300x229.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/mirandamods\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/02\/C21.jpeg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<address style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Image credit\u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/www.flickr.com\/photos\/bostworld\/\" rel=\"nofollow\">dbostromm<\/a>\u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/creativecommons.org\/licenses\/by-nc-sa\/2.0\/\" rel=\"nofollow\">CC Licence\u00a0<\/a><\/em><\/address>\n<h4><strong>March 1st 1630-1930<\/strong><\/h4>\n<p><em>\u201cI am absolutely committed to ensuring that our school system not only prepares pupils for this changing world, but also embraces the technological advances which are transforming education &#8220;. \u00a0Michael Gove, 2011<\/em><\/p>\n<p><em><\/em><strong>The Seminar<\/strong><br \/>\n<a title=\"mmshift2 by Learn4Life, on Flickr\" href=\"http:\/\/www.flickr.com\/photos\/learn4life\/6485979803\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http:\/\/farm8.staticflickr.com\/7159\/6485979803_e4d9e6d801.jpg\" alt=\"mmshift2\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" \/><\/a><br \/>\nThe Big Picture: Chris Yapp<br \/>\nVisual Learning and Digital Literacy:\u00a0 Theo Keuchel; John Cuthell<br \/>\nUsing Video as a curriculum tool: Leon Cych<br \/>\nCan every student hear? Learning and Hearing: Roger Turner<br \/>\nUsing Skype in learning contexts: Glenys Hart<br \/>\nMapping concepts collaboratively: Christina Preston<\/p>\n<p><strong>The Workshop<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Mapping concepts: building and sharing collaborative knowledge<br \/>\nAndrea Raiker and Christina Preston<\/p>\n<p>Some joined the MirandaMod through Flashmeeting.<\/p>\n<p>You can <a href=\"http:\/\/flashmeeting.e2bn.net\/fm\/f67e93-15022\">watch the replay<\/a>\u00a0of some of the Flashmeeting. You can also read transcripts of two chat streams: the <a href=\"http:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/mirandamods\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/02\/010312-FM-Transcript.pdf\">Flashmeeting Transcript<\/a>\u00a0and the <a href=\"http:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/mirandamods\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/02\/010312-Livestream-chat.pdf\">Livestream chat<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>Participants also helped to build a resource about the topic for others to share using the map below.<\/p>\n<div>\n<h3>Integrating 21st Century Skills into the classroom<\/h3>\n<\/div>\n<p><iframe style=\"overflow: hidden;\" src=\"http:\/\/www.mindmeister.com\/maps\/public_map_shell\/139440546\/integrating-21st-century-skills-into-the-classroom?width=600&amp;height=400&amp;z=auto\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\"><\/iframe><\/p>\n<p>Many thanks to <a href=\"http:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/researchexchange\/events-2\/university-of-bedfordshire-students\/\">Grant Chaney<\/a> and <a href=\"http:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/researchexchange\/events-2\/university-of-bedfordshire-students\/\">Haydn Robson<\/a>, students at the University of Bedfordshire, for their technical support during the session.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Integrating 21st century skill